'''''Tale of Four''''', ni filime ngufi yo muri [[Amerika]] yo muri 2017 iyobowe na Gabourey Sidibe nk'umukinnyi we wa mbere  ikanakorwa na Kia Perry, Lisa Cortes na Shannon Gibson<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/gabourey-sidibe-tale-of-four/</ref>.  filimi igenda izunguruka mubagore bane batandukanye bafite inzira enye zitandukanye aho igishekeje ubuzima bwabo bwose burahura<ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/the-tale-of-four/</ref>. Ishingiye ku ndirimbo ""Four Women" yaririmbwe na nyakwigendera umuririmbyi akaba n'umurwanashyaka wa politiki Nina Simone<ref>https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2010/10/175793/gabourey-sidibe-the-tale-of-four-movie-interview</ref>. 

Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Ledisi Young, Meagan Kimberly Smith, Dana Gourrier na Aisha Hinds<ref>https://www.blackfilm.com/read/2017/10/watch-gabourey-sidibe-short-the-tale-of-four-online/</ref>.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://www.blackwomendirectors.co/gabourey-sidibe</ref>  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Nzeri 2016 mu mujyi wa New York, muri New York hanyuma yerekanwa ku ya 25 Kamena 2017 mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Nantucket<ref>https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2010/10/175793/gabourey-sidibe-the-tale-of-four-movie-interview</ref> . Yatsindiye igihembo cya filimi ngufi nziza mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Urbanworld 2017<ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/gabourey-sidibe-talks-image-consciousness-entertainment-1016766/</ref>. 

